## What formats of session data can I use?
You can type notes directly, paste in a transcript, or upload audio for transcription (coming soon). All of this is linked to the athlete's profile and active goals.

## Is this just for athletic coaches?
Not at all. While wisegrowth supports athletic training, it's equally useful for executive coaching, creative mentorship, academic advising, or any other long-term support role.

## Is athlete data secure?
Yes. wisegrowth uses encryption at rest and in transit. We follow best practices for handling personal data, and we're committed to transparency and control for both coaches and athletes.
